{{Infobox airport | name = Bogandé Airport | IATA = XBG | ICAO = DFEB | type = Public | city-served = [[Bogandé]] | location = {{flag|Burkina Faso}} | elevation-f = 984 | elevation-m = 300 | coordinates = {{coord|12|58|53.165|N|000|09|45.407|W|region:BF_type:airport|name=Bogandé Airport (Bogandé)|display=inline,title}} | pushpin_map = Burkina Faso | pushpin_label= DFEB | pushpin_map_caption = Location of Bogandé Airport in Burkina Faso | r1-number = 11/29 | r1-length-f = 2,625 | r1-length-m = 800 | r1-surface = Dirt | footnotes = Source: Burkina Faso AIP<ref name = "ASECNA AIP">Entry for Banfora Airport in ASECNA AIP [http://www.ais-asecna.org/en/ad/ad2.htm] Accessed 2017-05-26</ref><ref name="Google">{{Google maps|url=https://maps.google.com/maps?ht=en&z=13&t=k&q=12.9814348220825,-0.16261300444603+%28Bogandé+Airport%29|title=location of Bogandé Airport|accessdate=2017-05-26}}</ref> }}
'''Bogandé Airport''' {{Airport codes|XBG|DFEB}} is a public use [[airport]] located near [[Bogandé]], [[Gnagna Province|Gnagna]], [[Burkina Faso]].
The airport is listed as DFEB in the official ASECNA Aernautical Information Publication for Burkino Faso but a search of the ICAO database does not confirm its 4-letter ICAO location indicator code.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.icao.int/safety/iStars/Pages/API-Data-Service.aspx|title=API Data Service|website=www.icao.int|language=en-us|access-date=2018-08-20}}</ref>
