'''Jilin Television ''' (JLTV, {{zh|s=吉林电视台|p=Jílín Diànshìtái}}) is a [[television network]] covering the [[Changchun]] city and [[Jilin]] province area. It was founded and started to broadcast on October 1, 1959. JLTV currently broadcasts in [[Standard Chinese|Chinese]], [[Manchu language|Manchu]], and [[Mongolian language|Mongol]].

